name: Ms. Zammi's Spaze Mizzion
description:
Disclaimer for mac users:  right click and open the game, first it'll show a popup 'mac cannot check malicious software' --> click on ok and then right-click open again, you can play the game then. [please bear since this project is in a prototype phase]

A space maze.

- Use arrow keys to move around.

- Level 1: Collect all the stars and then move to the next level.

- Level 2: Collect all the craters to win.
